<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.4">
<l>paraṉē pañcavaṉ pūḻiyaṉ cōḻaṉ pārmaṉ ṉarmaṉṉar tāmpaṇin tēttum</l>
<l>varaṉē mātava ṉēmatu cūtā maṟṟōr naltuṇai niṉṉalā lilēṉkāṇ</l>
<l>naraṉē nāraṇa ṉētiru naṟaiyūr nampī yemperu māṉumpa rāḷum</l>
<l>araṉē yātiva rākamuṉ ṉāṉā yaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Divine one, superior [lord] whom earth’s Pāṇṭiya, Pūḻiya [Cēra],</l>
<l rend="indent">and Cōḻa kings of kings humbly praise,</l>
<l>Mādhava, Madhusūdana, besides you, see,</l>
<l rend="indent">I have no other benevolent protector,</l>
<l>Nara, Nārāyaṇa, noble of Tirunaṟaiyūr, great lord, king who rules the heavens,</l>
<l>You who once became the primordial boar,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
